text.tspan: Join us at the openSUSE Summit at Coronado
Springs Resort, meet a Geeko, hang out,
discuss, hack and enjoy good company!
REGISTER NOW! @ Summit Website
www.summit.opensuse.org
Participate!
At the Sumit you can also be the main event.
You have something “Linux” you want to talk
about? This is your chance. Choose one of three
ways of sharing your involvement with Linux
and make of the Summit an even greater event!
Lighting talk 15 min, short talk 30 min,
presentation 50 min, workshop 1-4 hours.
At the openSUSE Summit 2013 (oSSum13) a
wide variety of Free and Open Source Software
contributors will gather to collaborate on one
of the major Linux distribution projects.
Disney’s Coronado Spring Resort
1000 West Buena Vista Drive
Lake Buena Vista, Florida 32830-8403
